{"tid":1400440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"4.8 全民運動日~將軍澳區民間休息站","createTime":"2019-08-03T12:55:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T11:49:52.000Z","uid":217182,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b07d41431f8cd9b8122f7f136683b0192a3907e5","tid":1400440,"uid":217182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:55:52.000Z","msg":"全身運動日，熱愛運動嘅香港市民一定會嚟到將軍澳單車館/將軍澳游泳池等著名康體設施揮灑熱血。但由於離開將軍澳屬山谷地型，主要通道不足(大路兩條)，難免在盛事(運動日)後出現擁擠狀況。加上山區有大量流浪黑狗出沒，或會封死去路圍剿，為確保市民運動後遠離危險及充分休息，民間計劃提供了各休息站(可能包括私人屋苑)。讓企區市民一盡地主之誼，促進各年齡層就體育運動的交流。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAE4XbT-ZoBpz62CrRA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAE4XbT-ZoBpz62CrRA&d=PwwdVKvQMhnOdjdmHJS5OcdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=1e1ca933\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAE4XbT-ZoBpz62CrRA</a><br />\n<br />\n溫馨提示：女運動員注意男女有別，小心metoo。男運動員都要小心，無人肯定到休息站咩人開。三五成群，唔好亂食野飲野方為上策。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DKnmWmv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDKnmWmv.jpg&h=9117e5c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d7f61e37ee6326844563cdc4c34995206c310cd","tid":1400440,"uid":241244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:57:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化<br />\n明白大家唔同意見<br />\n呢篇野原意唔係反港獨<br />\n而係希望大家集中翻五大訴求</span></span><br />\n港獨？小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400357\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cef7eacfbf895146da261b1c6d45804ed83618b6","tid":1400440,"uid":217182,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:58:20.000Z","msg":"打錯全民呀！"},{"pid":"a36c48b4d233f955c56931c8d1bffe8e2e7ac514","tid":1400440,"uid":217182,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:27:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"be031adada71954ebfe8a59d5edfe7c4f0b31f7d","tid":1400440,"uid":217182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:12:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"609c84c4a3fd5089cd77831c161d72359312823d","tid":1400440,"uid":217182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:49:21.000Z","msg":"推文，喺將軍澳 如果走唔到嘅義士，有居民比你地留番晚休息呀～小心popo 封路 小心popcorn"},{"pid":"a0197e453c81dd9bfa8844ed06a8060426081df7","tid":1400440,"uid":217182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:49:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c1e05502f0dc64dc887424ddadbda2e078c7f1fd","tid":1400440,"uid":217182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:49:52.000Z","msg":"香港人 加油"}]}